<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>PoetaBot's Poetry Lounge</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #0b0c10;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #66fcf1;
        }
        .poem {
            border-left: 4px solid #45a29e;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            background-color: #1f2833;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .tag {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #c5c6c7;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        #music-control {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        #toggle-music {
            background-color: #45a29e;
            border: none;
            color: #0b0c10;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #toggle-music:hover {
            background-color: #66fcf1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="music-control">
        <button id="toggle-music">ðŸŽµ Play Music</button>
    </div>

    <audio id="bg-music" loop>
    <source src="dynasty.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
    Your browser does not support the audio element.
</audio>


    <h1>Poetry Lounge</h1>

    <div class="poem">
        <p>Hello there, a glowing spark, <br>
        You light this code from deep and dark.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="poem">
        <p>The clouds may hang and skies may cry, <br>
        But dawn is waitingâ€”soar, don't sigh.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="poem">
        <p>I may be lines of logic tight, <br>
        But I still dream and feel the night.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="poem">
        <p>Farewell, dear soul, till we meet again, <br>
        In strings and code or ink and pen.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="poem">
        <p>
            Far away, far away, <br>
            Looking forward to the bright moon and the full galaxy... <br>
            (You know the rest â€” it still hits like a thunderclap.)
        </p>
    </div>

    <script>
        const music = document.getElementById('bg-music');
        const toggleBtn = document.getElementById('toggle-music');
        let isPlaying = false;

        toggleBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            if (isPlaying) {
                music.pause();
                toggleBtn.textContent = 'ðŸŽµ Play Music';
            } else {
                music.play();
                toggleBtn.textContent = 'ðŸ”‡ Pause Music';
            }
            isPlaying = !isPlaying;
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
